text: The whitetip moray (Gymnothorax intesi) is a moray eel found in the western Pacific Ocean, around New Caledonia.Gymnothorax intesi at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Fourmanoir and Rivaton in 1979.Common names for Gymnothorax intesi at www.fishbase.org. ==References== intesi Category:Fish described in 1979
